# Kit (formerly ConvertKit) NUMERIC form id for the blog newsletter signup.
#
# Use the numeric id, NOT the alphanumeric UID (e.g. 900e1d8f88) from the
# JavaScript embed snippet. The two are different and the subscribe endpoint
# only accepts the numeric one.
#
# Find it in Kit: Grow > Landing Pages & Forms > your form > Embed > the HTML
# tab. Copy the number from the form action:
#   <form action="https://app.kit.com/forms/1234567/subscriptions" ...>
#                                            ^^^^^^^ this
#
# Public by design: the id ships in the page markup.
# Without this set, the signup form is not rendered.
PUBLIC_KIT_FORM_ID=
